  <para>
    Expand the <link
    linkend="Section-Concepts-Microstructure-PixelSelection">pixel
    selection</link> in the &micro; called
    <varname>microstructure</varname> by selecting all pixels within a
    distance <varname>radius</varname> of a currently active pixel.
    The radius is given in units of the &micro; pixel size.  This is
    the opposite of <xref
    linkend="MenuItem-OOF.PixelSelection.Shrink"/>.
  </para>

